# QA gates

## Before PR (local only)

```bash
cd backend && composer validate --no-check-publish
cd backend && php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
cd backend && php artisan test
npm run build
git diff --check
```

Plus manual/local smoke:

- Backend: `http://127.0.0.1:8000/api` health + read endpoints 200.
- UI CRUD: shipments, managers, clients, checkpoints, finance status/export, Telegram save.
- Validation: 422 visible; API-down banner when backend stopped.
- No requests to production URLs during local QA.

Use skill: `.cursor/skills/local-regression-qa/SKILL.md`

## Before deploy

- PR merged or explicit user deploy instruction.
- No uncommitted secrets or `backups/` in commit.

## After deploy

- `GET /api/health` on Render URL.
- CORS from Vercel origin.
- Frontend uses production `VITE_API_BASE_URL`, not localhost.
- Spot-check CRUD ID-flow in browser.

Use skill: `.cursor/skills/deployment-verification/SKILL.md`
